{"tid":321141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開播了 俄  羅斯《飢餓遊戲》真人騷　殺人強姦照拍隨時被捕","createTime":"2017-07-14T05:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T01:02:36.000Z","uid":51965,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ca8a2b390bef8b65ee1f8189f269dc80ec67a2","tid":321141,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"【戰鬥民族】俄  羅斯《飢餓遊戲》真人騷　殺人強姦照拍隨時被捕<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有link可以睇 <br />\n利申 唔信有人會殺人 強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/60519/-%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF-%E9%A3%A2%E9%A4%93%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%A8%B7-%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%85%A7%E6%8B%8D%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F60519%2F-%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E9%25A3%25A2%25E9%25A4%2593%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2-%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A8%25B7-%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E7%2585%25A7%25E6%258B%258D%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&d=uVFOA7yN8pFPaKQo%2FJD7vP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d363216e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/60519/-%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF-%E9%A3%A2%E9%A4%93%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%A8%B7-%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%85%A7%E6%8B%8D%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95</a><br />\n<br />\n《飢餓遊戲》（The Hunger Games）竟然有真實版！俄羅斯富商Yevgeny Pyatkovsky推出名為《Game2: Winter》真人騷節目，將30名參賽者送到西伯利亞野外進行為期9個月的生存遊戲，爭奪130萬英鎊（約1256萬港元）的最終獎金。比賽規則寫到明容許一切行為，包括「打架、飲酒、吸煙甚至強姦殺人」。Pyatkovsky指製作方不會負任何責任：「就算他們被殺或者被強姦，都不能控告我們。」所有參賽者都要簽一份免責文件，上面寫明違反俄羅斯法例依然有機會被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n除了人類對手之外，參賽者還要面對西伯利亞熊和野狼，隨時受傷喪命。這個危險遊戲家庭觀眾都可以參與。每個星期參賽者會指定一件物資，由觀眾透過節目網站提供贊助，十足《飢餓遊戲》的橋段。《Game2: Winter》將在下年7月開播，現時已有60人報名參加，包括一名美國人。為打中國市場，節目還會有中文版，實在非常進撃。"},{"pid":"475a2ed6ab234f664a6962ebb149e1734028ec19","tid":321141,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed496c414a656e010cd6c39b9849faa18076c9d6","tid":321141,"uid":33840,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇連登仔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即刻比人隊冧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19650a0cda2951584a8c804f8812e35e8e72a8db","tid":321141,"uid":1425,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"諗起有套真人SHOW完左班人都唔知"},{"pid":"4cab64c5f7c3bfb24f0c69a2065fc906989b799b","tid":321141,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"單野好似成年前啦啵<br />\n印象中班人好和平咁完左個game<br />\n但有節目走數無獎金，好似係咁"},{"pid":"411788e9675b22e5d3691549b92b7266109292d5","tid":321141,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7271cadcda1abc385d1cee328f0865e5975700f","tid":321141,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"7月1號開播左 大家有冇link"},{"pid":"f682218fe8f95c1dbd987c29cee16a2c43a3550f","tid":321141,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【戰鬥民族】俄  羅斯《飢餓遊戲》真人騷　殺人強姦照拍隨時被捕<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有link可以睇 <br />\n利申 唔信有人會殺人 強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/60519/-%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF-%E9%A3%A2%E9%A4%93%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%A8%B7-%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%85%A7%E6%8B%8D%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" dat